{
  "__meta__": {
    "title":        "\"For Example\"",
    "subtitle":     "The Exemplary Journey.",
    "prompt_start": "Your time has come, press enter to begin...",
    "prompt_end":   "..."
  },

  "__main__": {
    "_": {
      "context": [
        "You stand at the foot of the cathedral, Exempli Gratia.",
        "The double-doors' stare pierces through you."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "text":      "Enter the cathedral.",
          "follow_up": "You enter.",

          "next": "main_hall-start"
        },
        {
          "text":      "Do not.",
          "follow_up": "You do not.",

          "hide_if": "resisted-0",

          "next": "ENDING-leave_immediately"
        },
        {
          "text":      "(You must enter.)",
          "follow_up": "(And you do.)",

          "show_if": "resisted-0",

          "next": "main_hall-start"
        }
      ]
    },

    "main_hall-start": {
      "context": [
        "You are in the main hall. The ceilings dizzy you.",
        "You feel at home, in spite of yourself."
      ],

      "choices": [
        { "text": "Let it wash over you.", "next": "extraction-0" },
        {
          "text":      "Leave.",
          "follow_up": "Behind you, a rhythmic thumping.",

          "hide_if": "resisted-0",

          "on_select": {
            "set": "resisted-0"
          },

          "next": "_"
        },
        {
          "text": "Try to leave.",
          "follow_up": [
            "You freeze. You can't.",
            "",
            "There is something you lost.",
            "(And something you gained.)"
          ],

          "show_if": "resisted-0",
          "hide_if": "resisted-1",

          "on_select": {
            "set": "resisted-1"
          },

          "next": "main_hall-start"
        }
      ]
    },

    "extraction-0": {
      "context": [
        "You look deeply into the architecture, seeing yourself in the murals and supporting beams.",
        "It brings you great fear not knowing what you will find - should you proceed."
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Continue.", "next": "extraction-1" },
        {
          "text": "Stop, while you can.",
          "follow_up": [
            "(Can you?)"
          ],

          "hide_if": "resisted-0",

          "on_select": {
            "set": [ "resisted-0" ]
          },

          "next": "main_hall-start"
        }
      ]
    },

    "extraction-1": {
      "context": [
        "You fall to your knees. Your vision blackens.",
        "There is a stinging wetness on your face.",
        "You feel a hot vapor engulfing you."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "text":      "Do nothing.",
          "follow_up": "...",

          "next": "extraction-last"
        },
        {
          "text": "Do something. (Have you no will?)",
          "follow_up": [
            "(Indeed you have none.)",
            "",
            "Nothing happened."
          ],

          "hide_if": "resisted-0",

          "next": "extraction-last"
        },
        {
          "text": "Do something. (Your will could be stronger.)",
          "follow_up": [
            "(But it was starved.)",
            "",
            "Nothing seemed to happen."
          ],

          "show_if": "resisted-0",
          "hide_if": "resisted-1",

          "on_select": {
            "set": "resisted-1"
          },

          "next": "extraction-last"
        },
        {
          "text": "Do something. (Your will is strong.)",
          "follow_up": [
            "(Perhaps strong enough.)",
            "",
            "Nothing seemed to happen."
          ],

          "show_if": "resisted-1",

          "on_select": {
            "set": "resisted-2"
          },

          "next": "extraction-last"
        }
      ]
    },

    "extraction-last": {
      "context": [
        "And you go numb.",
        "",
        "It deteriorates - what remains of your sense of self.",
        "Although, you feel as though you must allow it to happen.",
        "",
        "You must submit.",
        "You must not have will."
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-1", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" },
        {
          "text": "(Resist.)",
          "follow_up": [
            "You open your eyes. The incessant spinning lets up.",
            "",
            "You peer into the reflective stained-glass, and see yourself.",
            "You find your face covered in a silver, opaque substance.",
            "You remember its sting."
          ],

          "show_if": "resisted-1",

          "next": "main_hall"
        },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit.", "hide_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extracted"         },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" },
        { "text": "Submit?", "show_if": "resisted-2", "next": "ENDING-extraction_failed" }
      ]
    },

    "main_hall": {
      "context": [
        "That dim, orange twilight which once lit the room has now faded.",
        "All else remains changed; the hall is still.",
        "You are afraid."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Look around.",
          "follow_up": [
            "You look.",
            "",
            "...",
            "",
            "[and you see some stuff idk]"
          ],

          "hide_if": "looked_around",

          "on_select": {
            "set": "looked_around"
          },

          "next": "main_hall"
        },
        { "text":  "[interact w smthn you saw]", "show_if": "looked_around", "next": "main_hall" }
      ]
    },

    "ENDING-leave_immediately": {
      "context": [
        "You don't look back."
      ]
    },

    "ENDING-extracted": {
      "context": [
        "Of your life, you now infer that all but this one moment-",
        "",
        "This moment is all that matters now.",
        "         It is all.",
        "         It is all that matters.",
        "                   That matters.",
        "",
        "All that was before is now beneath you.",
        "                           Beneath you.",
        "",
        "You are not here, and yet you are.",
        "                          You are.",
        "You are not               you.",
        "",
        "(You failed to avoid extraction.)"
      ]
    },

    "ENDING-extraction_failed": {
      "context": [
        "You cannot keep your eyes closed.",
        "You                        lose.",
        "",
        "Your fear is too strong.",
        "Your ego would not die.",
        "You      would not die.",
        "",
        "You recall the wounds that which you hid from the world.",
        "And you realize that they are precisely what kept you here.",
        "    Recall      that they            hid          you.",
        "And you                   are                         here.",
        "    ",
        "",
        "(You narrowly avoided extraction.)"
      ]
    }
  }
